# Repo-root context — only need server/ + docs/renderer-spec.md.
# Default-deny by including everything we DON'T want in the image.
**/.git
**/.github
**/.claude
**/.venv
**/__pypackages__
**/.pdm-python
**/.pdm-build
**/dist
**/build
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.DS_Store
**/.idea

# Server-local
server/data-local/
server/.env
server/.env.*
server/uv.lock

# Firmware + deploy artifacts aren't needed in the server image
firmware/
deploy/
diary/

# Top-level docs except the one we ship
docs/*.md
!docs/renderer-spec.md
